metadata.name: Shima Enaga #1
metadata.description:
The Shima Enaga NFT collection represents unity and equality in all races, religions, and nationalities - much like DeFi itself. Featuring clothing, items, and backgrounds from all over the globe, each ShimaNFT is as unique as the Shima community itself! The collection of completely unique NFT’s is not only stunning artwork, but will also provide the following benefits:

 

 50% of royalties will be used to buy back NFT’s sold under floor value to maintain a healthy value 

 50% of royalties will go to marketing, developing, and building the Shima Enaga Academy
